{"tid":1635299,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想發起一個 #iHaveAdreamHK 運動","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T03:23:37.000Z","uid":170812,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b33c72e342c1d7f04bb3b88db0db34fcded6586","tid":1635299,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"事緣我響某FB page睇到個版主叫人留低光復香港之後，有咩<strong>夢想</strong>、或者<strong>想做嘅事</strong>，引起好多人留言，放低洋蔥，好多人睇到之後都話<strong>叉左電</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n跟住有人留言想將佢變成文宣運動，將呢種正能量散出去（借用<ins>馬丁。路德金</ins>名句，&ldquo;<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">I have a dream</span></strong>&quot; 做Tag）。我唔見有人做，於是膽粗粗嘗試做。（後來見到有文宣組將一啲留言畫左做文宣，應該冇衝突掛）<br />\n<br />\n點做呢？<br />\n1. 用紙/白板，簡單寫低你光復香港後嘅夢想/想做的事，甚至你可以畫畫、錄短片，諸如此類，總之發揮創意。<br />\n(可以考慮中英並用，咁可以上<strong>twitter</strong>戰線）<br />\n<br />\n2. 最尾加上 五大訴求，缺一不可 / 光復香港，時代革命 / 5Demands, Not1Less / Liberate HK, the Revolution of our time （重申香港人嘅訴求同團結一致）<br />\n<br />\n3. Tag <strong>#iHaveAdreamHK</strong> （可以tag 埋 <strong>#5DemandsNot1Less</strong>) <br />\n<br />\n4. Tag 3-5個friends做同樣嘅野<br />\n<br />\n5. 放上FB ， twitter<br />\n<br />\n我希望呢個活動，能夠俾<strong>全世界人</strong>知道香港人依然<strong>不放棄</strong>，依然<strong>團結</strong>，我地會<strong>堅定地走落去</strong>，直到<strong>光復香港</strong>，大家可以向自己嘅<strong>夢想</strong>進發。<br />\n<strong>希望各位支持。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去自己FB/twitter度做。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXuRkD6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXuRkD6.jpg&h=1d1be89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#iHaveAdreamHK"},{"pid":"a1a83ba9a02287a09c796f8ebabb0b0f34eabbbe","tid":1635299,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:07:46.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"8bb56d01b0d008a91b6834a7957d60f50190d7a2","tid":1635299,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:08:28.000Z","msg":"我知今晚出面開花<br />\n唔知有冇後排手足冇去，可以做其他行動"},{"pid":"3dba8535f6afa7e4569a1